                    <h2>Introduction</h2>
                    <p>
                        In the ever-evolving job market, distinguishing oneself with strong employability skills can be the difference between securing a high-paying position and settling for less. Employability skills are essential traits and competencies that enhance a candidate's appeal to employers. With the introduction of the KnocScore, a groundbreaking tool that measures an individual’s knowledge credibility within specific domains, business professionals now have a quantifiable metric to showcase their expertise to potential employers. This article explores how the KnocScore can be strategically used to enhance job search efficacy and secure better employment opportunities with higher compensation.
                    </p>
                    <p>
